qa_pairs.question: How do I get it? How do I set it up?
qa_pairs.answer: There's really not much for you to do. Like in that form on your PCR login page, if you see where it is, you fill that out. It makes a ticket.

qa_pairs.question: What happens after I fill out the form?
qa_pairs.answer: We'll have you confirm which database name in case you have more than one. Then we queue it up to have our server administrator re-index the database.

qa_pairs.question: Is it per user or per database?
qa_pairs.answer: It's not per user. It has to be enabled per database.

qa_pairs.question: How is recruiting going?
qa_pairs.answer: It's recruiting slow right now. I'm not happy about that. We just keep going one day at a time.
